{"tid":651280,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇睇AsNTM嘅絲打?","createTime":"2018-05-03T03:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T04:11:11.000Z","uid":164722,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"624c1d6ac58484427a5b64ddbf16426b1281bfe7","tid":651280,"uid":164722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"今年應該好快就出Cycle 6 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁喺出之前我地一齊重溫下cycle 1-5 啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nCycle 1個人覺得最好睇 好多靚女同埋個個都好易認 下面3個都係我當時鍾意嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/114031_233078e52b2c1b9d3dd3d0cd53fcfa31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F114031_233078e52b2c1b9d3dd3d0cd53fcfa31.jpg&h=4ef41291&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/114033_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F114033_7fdc1a630c238af0815181f9faa190f5.jpg&h=22d31b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/114036_8304eff8334b65eb5c133a1814f952a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F114036_8304eff8334b65eb5c133a1814f952a7.jpg&h=03f05ee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁當然我都有支持港女啦 不過香港人好似真係特別西 唔係埋唔到堆就係俾人排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/114238_26c40e9d52f43c3054242f589bdeac32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F114238_26c40e9d52f43c3054242f589bdeac32.jpg&h=08546845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我對Cycle 2同3其實都冇乜印象 淨係記得有個tvb嘅人同Tia都幾靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/114452_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F114452_704b27084030f0e97ce3ce3e5953e9e5.jpg&h=c5203318&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過都係Cycle1啲人靚啲 <br />\n<br />\nCycle 4 入面個香港人JB我真心覺得靚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過又係俾人排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/114624_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F114624_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=8051c638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢俾人foul嗰集我真係勁sad 根住我就冇再睇落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/03/114943_18e64d3ccb65aeefad87cbac90c6f461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F03%2F114943_18e64d3ccb65aeefad87cbac90c6f461.jpg&h=630cbe28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實都唔係咁差姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"339e946103d8b649fda0555a7ffd48c2df53df73","tid":651280,"uid":164722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}